7
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:09,910
I have to stop him. No matter what, I have to stop Yoon Seung Woo.

8
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:12,190
Hey, Yoon Seung Woo.

9
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,550
Let's talk.

10
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,460
Episode 19

